### ROI Analysis Formulas

#### Basic ROI Calculation
ROI = (Market Value - Total Cost) / Total Cost × 100

#### Example: Property 001
ROI = ($75,000 - $40,000) / $40,000 × 100 = 87.5%

#### Cash Flow Analysis
Monthly Cash Flow = (Rental Income - Expenses) - (Total Cost / 12)

#### Break-Even Analysis
Break-Even Months = Total Cost / Monthly Cash Flow

